so you can light them on fire.

00:00:05.460 --> 00:00:09.880
[Music]

00:00:09.880 --> 00:00:11.780
In the past, we've shown you
a fun way to make bubbles

00:00:11.780 --> 00:00:12.860
that you can hold down your hand,

00:00:12.860 --> 00:00:14.120
and light on fire.

00:00:14.540 --> 00:00:18.120
This is just a little bit of
bubble soap diluted with some water,

00:00:18.480 --> 00:00:20.880
and a can of butane that
I'm just turning upside down,

00:00:20.880 --> 00:00:22.640
and pressing onto
the bottom of the bowl.

00:00:22.880 --> 00:00:24.280
That releases the butane,

00:00:24.289 --> 00:00:26.119
it forms bubbles in the soap,

00:00:26.120 --> 00:00:28.180
you can then scoop them up onto your hands,

00:00:29.460 --> 00:00:30.740
and light them on fire.

00:00:31.260 --> 00:00:33.480
It's a cool trick that
